{"tid":1554532,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關於十一，大家都攰，但大家一定要入黎睇","createTime":"2019-09-09T04:17:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T04:27:05.000Z","uid":23046,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"068c031174867e590e89b917056dab7df484ec1f","tid":1554532,"uid":23046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T04:17:09.000Z","msg":"首先<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">十月一好撚重要</span></span><br />\n<br />\n非失敗主義<br />\n<br />\n而家每個六日都要出<br />\n老實講係人都攰<br />\n而且宣傳好似少左同<span style=\"color: blue;\">偏向左同溫層</span><br />\n見到呢幾次都係相對少人<br />\n<br />\n之前100萬200萬都係要大大力宣傳加有民陣召集<br />\n黎緊每個星期都唔知會發生咩事<br />\n而且太密喇，<br />\n亦係咁不斷開分支同不同地點活動<br />\n開始<span style=\"color: blue;\">資訊疲勞</span><br />\n所以係咪應該開始慢慢儲火力谷行10月1一齊出黎<br />\n同埋構思下要做咩同咩主題<br />\n舉美國英國旗？唱歌？<br />\n叫口號？<br />\n冇200萬都起碼整番150啦<br />\n<br />\n同埋果一日實會同藍屍硬砌<br />\n無論係網戰定實地戰，<br />\n如果唔夠多人，唔集中火力<br />\n可能會世界大亂，亦會有好多事發生。<br />\n好難預測。<br />\n<br />\n所以大家落力討論+宣傳下十一做咩啦<br />\n<br />\n雖然現時好多野要做要關注<br />\n但下下都準備唔夠就出戰<br />\nd力水越黎越唔夠<br />\n雖然10月1係重要<br />\n但抗爭係長期既<br />\n撐住呀香港人"},{"pid":"bbc7fb13944947801ade065975d64d08fe623565","tid":1554532,"uid":23046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T04:23:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7f47fe4e1df171de2808516ed21419c98563ab42","tid":1554532,"uid":23046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T04:24:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a2dc22ccace833a73a9e97955c4e32e2bd0c69a7","tid":1554532,"uid":23046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T04:24:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8613e3bc88d9ddd143f460273ce83e7272b5a76b","tid":1554532,"uid":23046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T04:25:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7b93350c90e03a0b3daf8319f1067de95685684d","tid":1554532,"uid":22506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T04:25:29.000Z","msg":"[國際戰線]今日已經係9月9號，係時候要籌備同宣傳9.29全球抗共遊行<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dQJtqS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dQJtqS</a>"},{"pid":"e599ec59304fc39dfe14a7e2e277b32037f09eab","tid":1554532,"uid":15193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T04:27:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}